## 5. DAILY WORKFLOW (P-WORK-01)
Ikuti pola sinkronisasi harian dari **[.agents/rules/03-DAILY-WORKFLOW.md](file:///D:/ERP-PJBM/.agents/rules/03-DAILY-WORKFLOW.md)**.

